es/885300378/image_885300378.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742083-pure-storage-q3-sell-this-spike-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 20:02:13"}, {"id": "4742080", "title": "Texas Instruments: A Hold Amid Solid Fundamentals And Growth Prospects", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Texas Instruments Inc (TI) HQ in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1173014771\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5902px\" height=\"3937px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Texas Instruments' (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TXN\" title=\"Texas Instruments Incorporated\">TXN</a></span>) current valuation seems fair relative to its peers. I believe its focus on long-term technology development, supported by significant investments in sustainable energy, makes the company a strong case for investors to hold the stock.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1173014771/image_1173014771.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742080-texas-instruments-a-hold-amid-solid-fundamentals-and-growth-prospects", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:56:52"}, {"id": "4742078", "title": "Intel: Prospects Of A New CEO Could Improve Sentiment (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Headquarters\" data-id=\"1831946092\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I've been <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4721924-intels-rebound-why-i-am-skeptical\">skeptical regarding</a> <strong>Intel</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) in prior analyses, and despite the constructive news of Pat Gelsinger's dismissal, I remain cautious about Intel's future. Nonetheless, releasing Pat Gelsinger from the CEO spot is a solid step. Therefore, I'm becoming more conservative about Intel's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742078-intel-prospects-of-a-new-ceo-could-improve-sentiment-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:45:47"}, {"id": "4742075", "title": "Four Growth Stocks For The Fourth Industrial Revolution", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Network Servers With Connections\" data-id=\"1313635551\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>You may have read some of my previous submissions to Seeking Alpha discussing growth stocks that stand to benefit from the Fourth Industrial Revolution, aka <a href=\"https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/mckinsey-explainers/what-are-industry-4-0-the-fourth-industrial-revolution-and-4ir\" rel=\"nofollow\">Industry 4.0</a>:</p> <blockquote><p>Industry 4.0\u2014also called the Fourth Industrial Revolution or 4IR\u2014is the next</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313635551/image_1313635551.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742075-four-growth-stocks-for-the-fourth-industrial-revolution", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:37:28"}, {"id": "4742053", "title": "Marvell Q3: Lofty Expectations Could Burn Investors (Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Marvell Technology office building in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1679337219\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Marvell FQ3: Stunning Beat-And-Raise</h2> <p><strong>Marvell Technology, Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MRVL\" title=\"Marvell Technology, Inc.\">MRVL</a></span>) investors who maintained their conviction in the stock have been well-rewarded. Accordingly, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4361537-marvell-technology-non-gaap-eps-of-0_43-beats-0_02-revenue-of-1_52b-beats-60m\">Marvell delivered a double beat</a> on revenue and adjusted EPS and also raised its guidance. The beat-and-raise</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742053-marvell-q3-lofty-expectations-could-burn-investors-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:30:01"}, {"id": "4742071", "title": "Carbios: Reflexivity Risks With Limited Catalysts Until 2026", "description": "<p><figure c