>our last article</a> from Turkey and China. There</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742071-carbios-reflexivity-risks-with-limited-catalysts-until-2026", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:22:52"}, {"id": "4742069", "title": "Google: Chrome Divestiture Selloff Was A Gift For Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Google office building in the Company\"s campus in Silicon Valley' data-id=\"1154834209\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5294px\" height=\"3529px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I had a 'Strong Buy' thesis on Google (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOGL</a></span>) in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723783-google-dont-miss-out-on-a-golden-discount\">September</a>. The stock did really well and outperformed the S&amp;P 500 until mid-November. However, the information regarding potential <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2024/nov/19/us-doj-sell-chrome-browser-ai-android\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Chrome divestiture</a> caused the stock price</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742069-google-chrome-divestiture-selloff-was-a-gift-for-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:14:26"}, {"id": "4742085", "title": "EUR/USD Hugs 1.0500 Ahead Of French No-Confidence Vote, Breakout Incoming?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial Stock Market Abstract Graph\" data-id=\"1370514197\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, htt